Description: Virtual machine management plugin for OpenMediaVault.
 omv-vmmanager provides a modern web UI for managing KVM/QEMU virtual
 machines via libvirt. It includes OVA import/export, backup, cloning,
 noVNC web console, and storage pool management. It runs as a Go
 backend and embeds a Svelte 5 frontend.
